Suppose we have a regular distribution 
\begin_inset Formula $f\{\phi\}$
\end_inset

 defined by the function 
\begin_inset Formula $f(\vec{x})=\begin{cases}
f_{1}(\vec{x}) & \vec{x}\in V\\
